import { Form, Field } from "react-final-form";

import { Container, Button, Grid, Paper, Typography } from "@material-ui/core";
import { TextField, Select } from "final-form-material-ui";

const Bookingform = () => (
  <Container style={{ padding: 16, margin: "auto", maxWidth: 800 }}>
    <Typography
      variant="h4"
      align="center"
      component="h1"
      style={{ padding: 16 }}
    >
      Parking Lot Management System !
    </Typography>

    <Form>
      <Paper style={{ padding: 16 }}>
        <Grid container justify="flex-start" alignItems="center" spacing={2}>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Field
              name="name"
              fullWidth
              component={TextField}
              type="text"
              label="Vehicle Number"
            />
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Field
              name="Entry_Time"
              fullWidth
              component={TextField}
              type="time"
              defaultValue="00:00:00"
              label="Entry Time"
            />
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} mt={4}>
            <Field
              name="Exit_Time"
              fullWidth
              component={TextField}
              type="time"
              defaultValue="00:00:00"
              label="Exit Time"
            />
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Field
              name="No Of Slots"
              fullWidth
              component={TextField}
              type="text"
              label="No Of Slots"
            />
          </Grid>

          <Grid
            container
            justify="space-evenly"
            alignItems="center"
            style={{ padding: 16 }}
          >
            <Button variant="contained" color="primary" type="submit">
              Submit
            </Button>
            <Button variant="contained" color="secondary" type="button">
              Reset
            </Button>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Paper>
    </Form>
  </Container>
);

export default Bookingform;
